      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BANDIT ALEX (3) goes very well over this track and trip including three wins. Scored by one length last time (29.92) in a Grade 5 over 520m at this track. Rates on top and should go close. BULL MARKET (8) could manage only second at this track last time but turned heads when posting an excellent 29.48 over 520m at this track three starts ago. Top win three back and rates a key player again. FASTENED (6) is a progressive type who recorded his 9th career win last time out (29.77) at this track. Solid winning record at this trip. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. VINTAGE GLOW (2) placed last start and is in the mix again.",
